trans-unit.source: Enumerates the elements of an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> の要素を列挙します。

trans-unit.source: To get an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract>, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A> method of an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract>.
trans-unit.target: 取得する、<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract>を使用して、<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A>のメソッド、<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract>です。

trans-unit.source: Returns the key and the value of the current <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> entry.
trans-unit.target: 現在の <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> エントリのキーおよび値を返します。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry" /> that contains the key and the value of the current <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> entry.
trans-unit.target: 現在の <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry" /> エントリのキーおよび値を保持する <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />。

trans-unit.source: After an enumerator is created or after the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> method is called, the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> method must be called to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before calling the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> method; otherwise, the return value of <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 列挙子を作成した後、または後に、<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A>メソッドが呼び出されると、<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>列挙子を呼び出す前に、コレクションの最初の要素に進めるメソッドを呼び出す必要があります、<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A>メソッド、それ以外の戻り値<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A>が定義されていません。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> also throws an exception if the last call to <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, which indicates the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> または例外をスロー、最後の呼び出し<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>返される`false`コレクションの末尾を示します。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> does not move the position of the enumerator, and consecutive calls to <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> return the same object until either <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> 連続して呼び出すと、列挙子の位置を移動しません<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A>されるまで、同じオブジェクトを返す<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>または<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A>と呼びます。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract" /> is positioned before the first entry of the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> or after the last entry.
